# pip install name's package                             install package
# pip uninstall name's package                           uninstall package
# pip install -u                                         install package and update it 
# pip list                                               list of packages and version that use in project
# pip list --outdated                                    list of packages and version that use in project and needs update
# pip list -o                                            list of packages and version that use in project and needs update
# pip freeze                                             list of packages and version that add to project
# pip freeze > requirements.txt                          add list of packages and version that add to project to requirements.txt file
# type  requirements.txt                                 return list of packages in requirements.txt file
# pip install -r requirements.txt                        install all packages in requirements.txt file